# Kiosk UI Application

This directory will contain the Angular + Nebular frontend application for the tablet kiosk interface.

**Purpose**: 
- Provides the guest-facing concierge interface
- Displays welcome screens, house manual, Wi-Fi info, local guide, and checkout instructions
- Runs in kiosk mode on the tablet
- Communicates with hub-api via SSE/WebSocket for real-time events

**Tech Stack**: Angular + Nebular UI framework

**Status**: Placeholder - Implementation begins in Slice 1

